WEBVTT

00:04.129 --> 00:05.387
Our work and our lives

00:05.389 --> 00:08.200
are based on certain
fundamental assumptions.

00:08.993 --> 00:11.286
Gravity holds us to the ground.

00:12.330 --> 00:14.289
Water is wet.

00:15.299 --> 00:19.568
No two human bite marks
are exactly the same.

00:24.709 --> 00:26.008
Derrick!

00:26.010 --> 00:27.609
Congratulations. Seriously, man.

00:27.611 --> 00:29.578
Congrats.

00:32.583 --> 00:34.850
We're all gonna be
working for you someday.

00:34.852 --> 00:37.219
All right, hold on.

00:37.221 --> 00:39.388
You're gonna need something
to wash this down with.

00:41.459 --> 00:43.525
What's this?

00:43.527 --> 00:44.960
Don't worry about it, man.

00:44.962 --> 00:46.425
