is make your teeth a bit whiter.

00:51.010 --> 00:53.068
Come on, we're all doing it.

00:59.571 --> 01:01.710
All right.

01:01.712 --> 01:03.579
My God.

01:05.786 --> 01:07.820
I just spotted my future wife.

01:07.822 --> 01:09.521
Go get her, man.

01:09.523 --> 01:11.990
Just walk up there, pretend
you want to order a drink.

01:11.992 --> 01:13.792
What do you have to lose?

01:13.794 --> 01:14.960
Come on, man.

01:14.962 --> 01:16.462
All right, all right, all right.

01:16.464 --> 01:18.063
Geez, get off me.

01:19.467 --> 01:20.599
Yes!

01:20.601 --> 01:21.834
All right.

01:21.836 --> 01:24.136
- Have a good night, man.
- You, too, my man.

01:24.138 --> 01:26.805
- We're free agents. Be good.
- Hey, thanks, man. Thank you.

01:26.807 --> 01:28.807
- Pleasure to meet you.
- Hey, congratulations. Good luck.

01:28.809 --> 01:30.242
- Thank you, thank you.
- Yeah, yeah.

01:30.244 --> 01:32.111
Take care. All right.

01:33.881 --> 01:37.483
Man.

01:37.485 --> 01:40.319
Wow. It's almost 2:00 in the morning.

01:40.321 --> 01:42.821
Need me to hail you a cab or something?

01:42.823 --> 01:44.656
