01:44.658 --> 01:45.958
Okay.

01:45.960 --> 01:48.293
Well, um, could I walk you?

01:48.295 --> 01:49.968
It's a free country.

01:52.054 --> 01:55.801
Listen, I like you, but...

01:55.803 --> 01:57.536
but I don't know you.

01:57.538 --> 02:00.639
So I think I should just go home, alone.

02:01.438 --> 02:03.408
Okay.

02:03.410 --> 02:06.645
Well, um, can I call you?

