02:24.431 --> 02:26.665
Let's not get ahead of ourselves.

02:26.667 --> 02:29.334
Just give me a call.

03:00.872 --> 03:02.000
Good night.

03:03.250 --> 03:05.103
Good night.

03:07.942 --> 03:10.209
And congrats on your promotion.

03:10.211 --> 03:14.713
Thanks, Miss 2125550161.

03:20.454 --> 03:22.087
I know, right?
I can't believe it, either.

03:22.089 --> 03:24.590
I'm convinced I'm gonna get
a call from upstairs saying that

03:24.592 --> 03:27.025
- it was all just a big mistake.
- Way to go, man. Congrats.

03:27.027 --> 03:28.327
I've actually been demoted.

03:28.329 --> 03:31.230
You'll make it to where I am one day.

03:31.737 --> 03:34.333
Hey, Grayden,
let me call you back, all right?

03:34.990 --> 03:36.802
Good morning.

03:36.804 --> 03:38.303
Mr. Graham?

03:38.305 --> 03:41.173
I'm Detective Bradley,
this is Detective Rue, NYPD.

03:41.175 --> 03:44.243
Hi. Can I help you?

03:44.245 --> 03:48.313
Well, um, I was hoping
I could ask you a few questions,

03:48.754 --> 03:50.515
about Ashley Richardson.

03:50.964 --> 03:52.718
Ashley?

03:54.635 --> 03:57.189
Mr. Graham. Can I get you anything?

03:57.191 --> 03:58.423
No, thanks, I'm okay.

03:58.425 --> 04:01.126
I, I'd just love to get to it.

04:01.128 --> 04:02.461
Got a promotion yesterday.

04:02.463 --> 04:05.564
A new job, and today's
my first day, so,

04:05.566 --> 04:07.856
