12:15.940 --> 12:18.138
since Thanksgiving.

12:19.377 --> 12:22.559
That you don't or won't
return my phone calls,

12:22.947 --> 12:25.061
not even at Christmas.

12:26.484 --> 12:31.354
So, please, just, I'm asking,
just call me back.

12:31.356 --> 12:34.390
Doesn't matter what time of day;
My phone's always on.

12:34.392 --> 12:37.693
Just... please.

14:23.735 --> 14:25.234
Hello, Anna?

14:25.236 --> 14:26.636
Congratulations.

14:26.638 --> 14:29.472
You've just won a Florida cruise!

14:30.808 --> 14:34.744
Man, nine years is a long time.

14:34.746 --> 14:36.779
Some of this stuff's pretty funky.

14:36.781 --> 14:39.582
Tell me about it.
What do you think this is?

14:42.286 --> 14:44.220
Well, those holes are
where the police lab

14:44.222 --> 14:45.988
cut out pieces for testing.

14:45.990 --> 14:48.124
The only DNA that they
recovered was Ashley's.

14:48.126 --> 14:49.546
Well, it's been nine years.

14:49.548 --> 14:51.994
Technology has improved since then.

14:51.996 --> 14:54.530
Might be worth giving it another go.

14:54.532 --> 14:56.799
Yes, of course I remember Derrick.

14:56.801 --> 14:58.801
He, showed a lot of promise.

14:58.803 --> 15:00.703
