15:00.705 --> 15:04.607
Do you remember his coworker,
Matt Williams?

15:05.843 --> 15:07.476
Sure.

15:07.478 --> 15:10.146
Matt got indicted a few years back.

15:10.148 --> 15:11.380
Insider trading.

15:12.270 --> 15:14.316
What about Josh O'Connor?

15:14.318 --> 15:17.119
Finally. Easy question.

15:17.121 --> 15:18.754
He's about six floors up.

15:18.756 --> 15:21.490
