15:57.327 --> 15:59.027
It's true, it's true.

15:59.029 --> 16:00.662
Derrick was always a perfect gentleman.

16:00.664 --> 16:02.931
He was the kind of guy
that would ask permission

16:02.933 --> 16:05.228
before he'd kiss a girl.

16:05.230 --> 16:06.801
So, I can count on you?

16:06.803 --> 16:09.304
Maybe come into my office
for a couple of hours,

16:09.306 --> 16:11.139
