16:11.141 --> 16:12.707
Of course.

16:12.709 --> 16:14.976
But what's gonna be different
about this trial?

16:14.978 --> 16:16.912
They got a new suspect or something?

16:16.914 --> 16:18.914
No, but bite mark evidence

16:18.916 --> 16:21.182
is starting to be recognized
for the junk science

16:21.184 --> 16:23.418
it's always been, and I'm hoping

16:23.420 --> 16:25.720
