16:43.403 --> 16:45.340
Been a while since I needed one of these.

16:46.155 --> 16:48.990
Can't even imagine what it's like

16:48.992 --> 16:50.512
to wake up every day and realize

16:50.514 --> 16:53.048
that you're in prison
for something you did not do.

16:53.803 --> 16:56.624
It's actually kind of reassuring
to hear you say that.

16:57.020 --> 16:58.853
There are days I forget.

16:58.855 --> 17:02.190
Days I convince myself
prison is where I belong.

17:02.192 --> 17:03.725
Has to be.

17:04.173 --> 17:05.794
Otherwise...

17:06.425 --> 17:08.229
why am I there?

17:08.231 --> 17:10.432
What about a support system?

17:10.434 --> 17:11.900
Friends? Family?

17:11.902 --> 17:13.068
