17:13.598 --> 17:15.069
Well, there must be someone.

17:15.071 --> 17:16.538
Didn't I hear you have a sister?

17:16.540 --> 17:18.205
When's the last time you spoke to her?

17:18.208 --> 17:20.275
I haven't seen or spoken
to anyone from before

17:20.277 --> 17:21.566
since they locked me up.

17:22.613 --> 17:24.068
Just better for me.

17:24.647 --> 17:26.112
Better for everyone.

17:26.650 --> 17:29.484
Does your family know what's going on?

17:29.486 --> 17:31.886
That we're trying to get you a new trial?

17:31.888 --> 17:34.923
It's always good to have
your people in the audience.

17:34.925 --> 17:37.325
The judge and the jury will notice.

17:38.929 --> 17:40.918
I don't know what to tell you.

17:43.900 --> 17:46.035
All right, I'lll'll make some calls.

17:46.037 --> 17:49.504
A.D.A. Madden's own expert, Dr. Novak,

17:49.506 --> 17:51.773
has withdrawn her initial opinion

17:51.775 --> 17:54.409
about the validity
of the bite mark impressions.

17:54.411 --> 17:56.745
